Michael Whaley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Michael_Whaley 0 Michael Whaley is an American film and television actor. He graduated from Culver City High school in 1980. Some of his most known characters are Dr. Wesley 'Wes' Hayes on Sisters, Det. Nathan Brubaker on Profiler, Detective Paul Armstrong on Early Edition, and Detective Carlton on CSI: Miami.
